This library is written as an improvement to SDL functionality with attempt to use SDL utilities in object-oriented, programmer-friendly graphic application API.
The code available on GitHub requires SDL 2.0.9 to function and comes without SLD files.

SDL webpage is available here: https://www.libsdl.org/index.php .

SDL 2.0 is created by Sam Lantinga and comes available under the zlib license :

